room_title: Escape room "Ancestors" by Breakout Escape Rooms in Riverside
room_description:
The beginning of the game takes you to the distant 11th century – the times of knights and crusades. You will need to go through the Heavenly Labyrinth to move from the distant past to one of the most mysterious stories of the twentieth century. You’ll see with your own eyes how the mystical legend of a man who turned the world is born.

1.Learn the generic name.
2.Collect the map of Nordic races.
3.Learn the practice of Seyd.
4.Get acquainted with the activity of the secret society.
5.Return the ancestors of heraldic symbols.
6.Decide the course of the battle of the XV century.
7.Collect 4 artifacts
